data.description: Welcome to your 4/2 home with a 2-car garage on this well-maintained property.  The one-story layout provides great living space with an open floor plan.  There is a breakfast bar in the kitchen, as well as, a dining room that serves for sit-down meals.  The sliding doors off the dining area are to the enclosed lanai where you can enjoy reading, working, or sipping your favorite beverage while relaxing in the privacy of your fenced-in backyard.  The backyard is large enough to build a pool as well.  The primary bedroom is located at the back of the home and has an ensuite bathroom. There are three additional bedrooms with a second bathroom.  The bedrooms have carpet and the living areas have vinyl flooring.  The laundry room is indoors with shelving for storage.  Make an appointment to see this home today!
